text: Dunfermline Athletic Football Club are a Scottish football team based in Dunfermline, Fife, commonly known as just Dunfermline. They play at East End Park and are nicknamed The Pars. They are currently managed by Neil Lennon who was given the job on a temporary basis in March 2025. ==References== Category:Scottish football clubs Category:1885 establishments in the United Kingdom Category:1880s establishments in Scotland
